{"tid":470892,"cid":23,"subCid":0,"title":"有時俾建議朋友都有啲唔知點嘅感覺","createTime":"2017-11-16T17:34:19.000Z","updateTime":"2017-11-22T11:29:27.000Z","uid":62063,"like":37,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":29,"replies":[{"pid":"f5de01dca55e8e2d89bfb8cabca1186c3fd1fb20","tid":470892,"uid":62063,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-16T17:34:19.000Z","msg":"1. <strong>大多覺得機靚=相靚</strong><br />\n未玩過已經一開波考慮旗艦機，但係完全忽略鏡頭同技術嘅因素，相信各位睇攝台幾位大師嘅相都會明白買機唔包送技術。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n2. <strong>單反好過無反</strong><br />\n覺得單反睇落專業啲，相都自然會靚啲，再加上唔少人覺得拎單反型啲pro啲，所以通常直接問邊部單反好。另一邊嘅無反，唔知點解十個有八個都覺得無反細部=廢啲。其實無反技術已經成熟，某啲方面甚至已經超越單反，<br />\n利申：兩樣都有，唔係倒單反米<br />\n<br />\n3. <strong>唔諗住學點用部機/攝影</strong><br />\n頭兩樣冇研究開有誤解其實都好正常嘅(?) 又或者係虛榮心作怪啦，高階機、貴機、睇落pro啲。解答哂啲疑惑之後揀啱心水機，點知拎到部機返嚟係長用Auto mode，之後又話手震(快門過慢）、太高太暗、景深時有時冇...etc。想教下佢地點用啲基本settings又話用Auto夠喇唔洗搞咁多嘢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n見當初佢地問得咁仔細以為係認真玩，點知<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n4. <strong>唔信筆直要預返少少買配件</strong><br />\n個筆直預到貼一貼，啱啱好買到機鏡。之後要買SD卡丶後備電丶腳架丶filter又話超哂筆直<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n不過有啲幫到都幾好，之後可以一齊出動再互相交流下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n大家又試過遇到啲咩事？分享下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"847eb4a491f46ebf6b46d64f3339930a124af788","tid":470892,"uid":45788,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-16T17:37:03.000Z","msg":"香港人邏輯：裝備&gt;技術"},{"pid":"f9fdff0720624afba73bdaad2268009c2b99bb2e","tid":470892,"uid":76005,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-16T17:40:24.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>香港人邏輯：裝備&gt;技術</blockquote><br />\n <br />\n現實：創意（概念）&gt;技術&gt; 裝備"},{"pid":"88420862dfc0a85661142e527571e4eb27d1f6cf","tid":470892,"uid":36157,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-16T17:41:25.000Z","msg":"難得咁有心<br />\n正個皮先"},{"pid":"dea72022b65b2ba6f19cc3e0dc30aeb5adee6c12","tid":470892,"uid":62063,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-16T17:41:29.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>香港人邏輯：裝備&gt;技術</blockquote><br />\n都係，玩幾樣嘢都見唔少"},{"pid":"d3ecd19004da47dcfd0c869ddb3ebc1648f50e27","tid":470892,"uid":136044,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-16T18:14:41.000Z","msg":"比錢  係買個虛榮  唔係買影靚相既裝備<br />\n<br />\n其實佢唔主動去學  已經知道醉翁之意不在酒<br />\n樓主只需要代相機公司多謝佢地  其他無謂多講<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"74f9b675c870c5662722d28ba1b073dd36bd4aa8","tid":470892,"uid":136044,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-16T18:16:13.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>比錢  係買個虛榮  唔係買影靚相既<del>裝備</del>工具<br />\n<br />\n其實佢唔主動去學  已經知道醉翁之意不在酒<br />\n樓主只需要代相機公司多謝佢地  其他無謂多講<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n樓上將裝備比喻成得個樣  冇實質作用既相機<br />\n咁我用工具區分返好D<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8fd499cc2d1bd8950cb43f145220e10744037f6a","tid":470892,"uid":143582,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-17T02:02:44.000Z","msg":"細部=相唔夠靚<br />\n要大大部掛頸，顯得專業"},{"pid":"51d5782dd6c6c724ea9b6bab074186645449ba38","tid":470892,"uid":117044,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-17T02:10:08.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"2f34e56d6d138c30fa1d955000db46dca11afd10","tid":470892,"uid":149200,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-17T02:32:08.000Z","msg":"我有個fd po ig會強調係用a7ii影<br />\n之後佢d傻朋友就會: a7ii!!! 呢部影出黎既相好靚！<br />\n又會話sony色彩鮮豔<br />\n見到呢d cm真係好傷眼<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"34d517ba5b748ed8a3869d2e8bb570875c16e22c","tid":470892,"uid":149200,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-17T02:38:53.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>細部=相唔夠靚<br />\n要大大部掛頸，顯得專業</blockquote><br />\n同埋影相要前清後朦呀<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9621b46398e79b7a70eca1f95967541f9753c65a","tid":470892,"uid":62063,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-17T02:48:53.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>細部=相唔夠靚<br />\n要大大部掛頸，顯得專業</blockquote><br />\n同埋影相要前清後朦呀<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n呢樣都多"},{"pid":"37194e130f8bedbdd752cc6c8877a9937703470c","tid":470892,"uid":50502,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-17T02:51:51.000Z","msg":"識就唔會問你啦 <br />\n<br />\n直接答佢我唔想教你囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b94664671f68b2265df62794f1a172b20f0e81e4","tid":470892,"uid":156771,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-17T03:13:14.000Z","msg":"第4項其實都係你班比意見既仆街做成<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n例如人地話想買部100d,<br />\n之後就會聽到一句<br />\n與其買100d，倒不如加多少少錢買200d,<br />\n跟手下一次又會話，與其買200d，倒不如加多d錢買xxxx<br />\n然後呢個步驟不停重複<br />\n搞到個budget由2千其就變到四千幾<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n咁仲邊預算買其他野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n到最後走黎同我講一句，如果你真心學攝影既，倒不如一步到位買高階機<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n心裡面真係一萬句粗口<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6ddc290bfa0d92ade9b9cdc413afeea4444e242d","tid":470892,"uid":62063,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-17T03:16:39.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>第4項其實都係你班比意見既仆街做成<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n例如人地話想買部100d,<br />\n之後就會聽到一句<br />\n與其買100d，倒不如加多少少錢買200d,<br />\n跟手下一次又會話，與其買200d，倒不如加多d錢買xxxx<br />\n然後呢個步驟不停重複<br />\n搞到個budget由2千其就變到四千幾<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n咁仲邊預算買其他野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n到最後走黎同我講一句，如果你真心學攝影既，倒不如一步到位買高階機<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n心裡面真係一萬句粗口<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我會叫人買入門機/中階機玩住先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n反正而家啲入門機唔差，高階機又貴又難操控(for新手）"},{"pid":"e9b83d7a203be6fedc21fa779e3f867b3c243d69","tid":470892,"uid":36157,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-17T03:25:55.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我有個fd po ig會強調係用a7ii影<br />\n之後佢d傻朋友就會: a7ii!!! 呢部影出黎既相好靚！<br />\n又會話sony色彩鮮豔<br />\n見到呢d cm真係好傷眼<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n以前nikon啲人都係咁<br />\n一開口教你買條炮，2.8，<br />\n果陣諗住頂到盡七八千蚊，<br />\n啲人一來就&ldquo;唔用nikon你永世都影垃圾&ldquo;<br />\n&ldquo;幾千蚊機/鏡買來做乜？&ldquo;<br />\n&ldquo;閃光燈我配埋個電源可以連閃過千次&ldquo;<br />\n（果陣未流行拍片）<br />\n&hellip;&hellip;之類<br />\n<br />\n宜家變成另一個brand<br />\nnikon人反而謙厚過以前（可能係）<br />\n<br />\n<blockquote>sony色彩鮮豔</blockquote><br />\n執過相 所有相機都係色彩鮮豔<br />\n<br />\nsony色彩鮮豔？<br />\n係嘅，某五毛直出相不知幾靚<br />\n唔好search佢相簿呀～"},{"pid":"63d7a87ab2791565e50f84fd9aaf4b49bd15a9ee","tid":470892,"uid":36157,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-17T03:29:10.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><br />\n反正而家啲入門機唔差，高階機又貴又難操控(for新手）</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n係，起碼熟習下個控制，諗返個光圈/快門，嘗試唔同環境下點做，咁先有用。<br />\n<br />\n真係有錢就請人影<br />\n相機純粹買來儲<br />\n點會用？<br />\n你睇treegun儲幾多"},{"pid":"3004ddf505a19d920e32fd105824ae4bd1c38b3e","tid":470892,"uid":104387,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-17T03:35:12.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>第4項其實都係你班比意見既仆街做成<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n例如人地話想買部100d,<br />\n之後就會聽到一句<br />\n與其買100d，倒不如加多少少錢買200d,<br />\n跟手下一次又會話，與其買200d，倒不如加多d錢買xxxx<br />\n然後呢個步驟不停重複<br />\n搞到個budget由2千其就變到四千幾<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n咁仲邊預算買其他野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n到最後走黎同我講一句，如果你真心學攝影既，倒不如一步到位買高階機<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n心裡面真係一萬句粗口<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我會叫人買入門機/中階機玩住先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n反正而家啲入門機唔差，高階機又貴又難操控(for新手）</blockquote><br />\n高階機d制擺晒出又頂mon又轉盤邊忽難操控？<br />\n新手入menu搵黎搵去叫易操控？"},{"pid":"e9d12fdda74dd063a497866162c51ac7fa8f39e1","tid":470892,"uid":8260,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-17T03:40:53.000Z","msg":"留名學嘢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/photo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e98c44e805ce7d5cb178456fb9bf5c134a1fc15f","tid":470892,"uid":28001,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-17T03:47:51.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>香港人邏輯：裝備&gt;技術</blockquote><br />\n <br />\n現實：創意（概念）&gt;技術&gt; 裝備</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n根本就係<br />\nLara Jade 用麵包超人相機影啲相都靚過啲 30萬係在大師<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=jDAnNjRJxOQ\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DjDAnNjRJxOQ&d=q81vSNv%2F1E6q%2FqP0Jqdngtr9upuAghWR75VkZoMWgf8%3D&h=bb61a098\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=jDAnNjRJxOQ</a>"},{"pid":"b7dd73ba858cd900289a5df7a92878bd9b33949a","tid":470892,"uid":36157,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-17T03:52:59.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><br />\n高階機d制擺晒出又頂mon又轉盤邊忽難操控？<br />\n新手入menu搵黎搵去叫易操控？</blockquote><br />\n我早排拎架600d上手唔識用<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n我覺得係習慣左就冇問題<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05